      • calcInteger

        public int calcInteger(int index)
        Description copied from class: CalcSeries
        Primitive equivalent to CalcSeries.calc(int). This allows for more efficient implementations of CalcSeries.updateView(Object) if a primitive type is stored. This implementation throws an UnsupportedOperationException.
        Overrides:
        calcInteger in class CalcSeries.IntSeries
